title: The Museum of Modern Art - New York (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The Museum of Modern Art New York
Harry N. Abrams | 1997 | ISBN: 0810981874 | English | 616 pages | PDF | 99.4 MB

Containing more than one thousand illustrations, many in full color, an extensive overview of the entire collection of The Museum of Modern Art includes works from all six of its departments--Painting and Sculpture, Drawings, Prints and Illustrtaed Books, Architecture and Design, Photography, and Film and Video
